chomsky.cellule

Class Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • chomsky.cellule.Cell

  • public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a cell of the array used by the CYK algorithm Each cell contains zero, one or many non terminal symbol
